    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">DEFINITION: Relates a party to something that it possesses and controls.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">NOTE: The ultimate form of ownership is the right to destroy.</rdfs:comment>
